      <description></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This is the first post on our brand-new <strong>tech blog</strong>. We've migrated from a legacy stack and we're excited to share what's next.</p><h2>What changed</h2><ul><li>Faster deploys</li><li>Better content tooling</li><li>Cleaner archives</li></ul><blockquote><p>Static hosting + a smart admin = the best of both worlds.</p></blockquote><p>Stay tuned — much more coming soon.</p>]]></content:encoded>
